聆听枪炮玫瑰乐队 (Guns N' Roses) 的新单曲《The General》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-guns-n-roses-soaring-new-single-the-general-3556059?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-guns-n-玫瑰飞翔新单身将军Elizabeth AubreyFri, 08 Dec 2023 10:53:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3556059 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="枪与玫瑰乐队" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是《也许》的B面</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-guns-n-roses-soaring-new-single-the-general-3556059">《聆听枪炮玫瑰》飙升的新单曲《The General》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="枪与玫瑰乐队" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Guns-N-Roses-Credit-Photo-by-Luis-Gutierrez_Norte-Photo_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a>今天分享了一首缓慢燃烧、飙升的新单曲，名为“The General”——请在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/slash-glastonbury-guns-n-roses-horror-movie-the-breach-3463459">Slash 谈论格拉斯顿伯里音乐节、枪炮玫瑰乐队和血腥的新恐怖电影《The Breach》</a></strong></li></ul><p> 《The General》是乐队限量版七英寸黑胶单曲《Perhaps》的 B 面，该单曲于 8 月开始接受预订。</p><p>乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-guns-n-roses-debut-new-song-the-general-in-los-angeles-3530190">上个月在洛杉矶首次现场表演了这首歌</a>，并于八月首次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-tease-another-new-song-the-general-set-to-arrive-in-october-3485958">预告了</a>这首歌。这场演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-announce-hollywood-bowl-shows-with-the-black-keys-3511949">标志着好莱坞露天剧场两晚的第一晚</a>。这是他们自 2021 年以来首次在洛杉矶比赛，也是他们第一次在这座标志性场地比赛。</p><p>在这里查看“将军”： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Guns N&#39; Roses - 将军（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/35IMLsf54oI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>乐队于今年夏天在匹兹堡的 PNC 公园<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-finally-release-new-song-perhaps-listen-3485004">于 8 月 18 日发行歌曲</a>后首次表演了《也许》。</p><p> “请原谅我，如果我没有四处奔走并试图做出那么多的表现，因为我会尝试弄清楚如何他妈的现场演唱它，”主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/axl-rose">Axl Rose</a>在介绍这首歌时说道。 “我喜欢回想当我们写这首歌时，它就像完美的开始。”</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/uk-favourite-guitar-riff-revealed-3552047">Sky Arts 在全新的三部分纪录片系列中展示了英国最受欢迎的吉他即兴演奏，<em>最伟大的吉他即兴演奏</em>和枪与玫瑰名列榜首。</a></p><p> 2000 名乐迷参与的民意调查将“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-sweet-child-o-mine-surpasses-one-billion-streams-on-spotify-3014987">Sweet Child O&#39; Mine</a> ”评选为史上最佳即兴重复段。这首歌曲于 1988 年 6 月发行，很快就登上了美国 Billboard Hot 100 排行榜的榜首，成为该摇滚乐队唯一的美国冠军单曲。这首歌还在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-lists/best-songs-of-all-time-1224767/guns-n-roses-sweet-child-o-mine-1225250/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>2021 年<em>有史以来最伟大的 500 首歌曲</em>排行榜上排名第 88 位。</p><p>早在六月，乐队就登上了格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的头条新闻。在 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/guns-n-roses-live-at-glastonbury-photos-setlist-3460919">对该节目的三星级评论</a>中， <em>《NME》</em>将该剧描述为“近年来最强大的剧目之一”，但由于它被交付给“错误的人群”，因此反响平平。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-guns-n-roses-soaring-new-single-the-general-3556059">《聆听枪炮玫瑰》飙升的新单曲《The General》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
